{"lemma":"صِغَرُ","slug":"صِغَرُ","root":"ص.غ.ر","root_slug":"ص-غ-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-غ-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24373","n24377","n24378"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%90%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become small, little","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be too small, young","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become insignificant or trifling","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be despised, humiliated or disgraced","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be narrow in thinking (of one's mind)","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be younger (than)","tags":["intransitive","transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"صَغَرَ أَحْمَدُ فَاطِمَةَ","english":"Ahmad was younger than Fatima."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to diminish, to make smaller, to reduce in size","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to belittle","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make diminutive, to change into the diminutive form","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَغُرَ (ṣaḡura) (form I), smallness, littleness","tags":["form-of","intransitive","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"young age, childhood","tags":["intransitive"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ص غ ر (ṣ ḡ r). From Proto-Semitic *ṣaɣir-. Cognate with Biblical Hebrew צָעַר (ṣāʿar, “to be small, insignificant”) and Akkadian 𒌉."},"ipa":["/sˤa.ɣu.ra/","/sˤiɣir/","/sˤa.ɣa.ra/","/sˤaɣ.ɣa.ra/","/sˤi.ɣar/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24373","headword_ar":"صَغُرَ","root":"Sgr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sagira","text_ar":"صَغِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SigarN","text_ar":"صِغَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) of the former, (S, Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagaArapN","text_ar":"صَغَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) also of the former, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagarN","text_ar":"صَغَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SugoraAnN","text_ar":"صُغْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, K,) which are both of the latter; (TA; [but Ibr D thinks that there is no reason for this assertion with respect to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SgrAn","text_ar":"صغران"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, small,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SigarN","text_ar":"صِغَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being the contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kibarN","text_ar":"كِبَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiZamN","text_ar":"عِظَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagaArapN","text_ar":"صَغَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]: (M, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SigarN","text_ar":"صِغَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corporeal substance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Aljiromi","text_ar":"فِى الجِرْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in years,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"age;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sagura","text_ar":"صَغُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with this inf. n., said of a human being, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was a child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the state of childhood, not having attained to puberty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagaArapN","text_ar":"صَغَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in estimation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rank"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dignity"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Alqadori","text_ar":"فِى القَدْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (M, K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sagura","text_ar":"صَغُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SigarN","text_ar":"صِغَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagaArN","text_ar":"صَغَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagaArapN","text_ar":"صَغَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SugoraAnN","text_ar":"صُغْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SugorN","text_ar":"صُغْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagarN","text_ar":"صَغَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was content with vileness, baseness, abasement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignominy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyranny,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"injury:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagarN","text_ar":"صَغَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sagira","text_ar":"صَغِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, vile, base,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignominious;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SugorN","text_ar":"صُغْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagaArN","text_ar":"صَغَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagaArN","text_ar":"صَغَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being small,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little, in estimation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rank"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dignity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sagura fiY Euyuwni Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"صَغُرَ فِى عُيُونِ النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, meaning, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became small,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little, in the eyes of men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he lost his reverence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reverend dignity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [See also 6.] One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yaSoguru Eano ka*aA","text_ar":"هُوَ يَصْغُرُ عَنْ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, is smaller than,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"too small for, such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaqil~u","text_ar":"يَقِلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ql","text_ar":"قل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sagurato Eani Alwaladi","text_ar":"صَغُرَتْ عَنِ الوَلَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was too young to bear offspring"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jl","text_ar":"جل"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA SagaraniY A_il~aA bisanapK","text_ar":"مَا صَغَرَنِى اـِلَّا بِسَنَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Sagura Ean~iY","text_ar":"مَا صَغُرَ عَنِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was not younger than I, save by a year"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sagurati Al$~amosu","text_ar":"صَغُرَتِ الشَّمْسُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun inclined to setting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","IAar","M","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n24377","headword_ar":"صُغْرٌ","root":"Sgr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagaArN","text_ar":"صَغَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, (S, [and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1692},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the Kur vi. 124,]) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SugaArN","text_ar":"صُغَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, (Msb, [but perhaps there is an omission in my copy of the Msb after this word,]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SagarN","text_ar":"صَغَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vileness, baseness, abasement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignominiousness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb:) so the second word signifies in the Kur vi. 124: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyranny,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oppression,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"injury."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumo EalaY","text_ar":"قُمْ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sugorika","text_ar":"صُغْرِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sagarika","text_ar":"صَغَرِكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rise thou, notwithstanding thy vileness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignominiousness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) [See also 1, of which it is an inf. n.]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n24378","headword_ar":"صَغَرٌ","root":"Sgr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SugorN","text_ar":"صُغْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. [And see 1, of which it is an inf. n.]"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}